title: Blac Chyna Spotted Without Engagement Ring on Date With Mystery Man She Also Stepped Out With on Super Bowl Sunday
text:
Ciara and Her Baby Bump Dance to Whitney’s ‘I’m Every Woman’ Kardashians Blac Chyna Spotted Without Engagement Ring on Date With Mystery Man She Also Stepped Out With on Super Bowl Sunday February 11, 2017 @ 12:57 PM By Nicholas Hautman 
Blac Chyna was spotted without her engagement ring while enjoying a lunch date with a mystery man in West Hollywood on Friday, February 10. The unidentified plus-one was the same man Chyna cozied up to during the Super Bowl , a source tells Us Weekly . PHOTOS: Rob Kardashian and Blac Chyna’s Cutest Moments 
The 28-year-old model, who is engaged to Rob Kardashian , and the mystery fellow sat opposite each other while dining at a Japanese restaurant. She kept a low profile in a blue Adidas tracksuit and a black beanie, arriving in the not-so-subtle $200,000 purple Lamborghini that Kardashian, 29, bought for her last year. Blac Chyna was spotted at lunch with a new man, on Friday, February 10, 2017. X17 Online 
The lunch date came less than a week after Chyna was spotted getting close to the same guy at Estrella's MA Theater in Los Angeles while watching the New England Patriots defeat the Atlanta Falcons in Super Bowl LI on Sunday, February 5. A source told Us the duo sat so close together that they looked like a couple. The insider also overheard Chyna telling a friend that she's "still with Rob" but that they aren't living together.
